  <body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="date">Last updated: March 26, 2026</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>Bible Tea collects minimal data to provide and improve the app experience:</p>
    <p><strong>Account data:</strong> When you create an account, we store your email address and authentication token via Clerk.</p>
    <p><strong>Usage data:</strong> Listening progress, streak data, and preferences are stored to sync your experience across devices.</p>
    <p><strong>Anonymous analytics:</strong> We collect anonymous usage data to understand which features are popular and improve the app.</p>

    <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. We do not track you across other apps. We do not share your data with advertisers.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <p><strong>Clerk</strong> — Authentication. <a href="https://clerk.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    <p><strong>RevenueCat</strong> — Subscription management. <a href="https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    <p><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — Infrastructure. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/">Privacy Policy</a></p>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored on Cloudflare's global network. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You can request deletion of your account and all associated data at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:hello@truemythgames.com">hello@truemythgames.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@truemythgames.com">hello@truemythgames.com</a>.</p>
  </body>
